iversity-support">Equality and diversity support</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #bd1f4f" href="/the-hospice/our-services/learning-disability-support">Learning disability support</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #bd1f4f" href="/the-hospice/our-services/the-art-room">The art room </a></li></ul></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #523b6b" href="/the-hospice/work-here">Work here</a><ul class="subs"><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #523b6b" href="/the-hospice/work-here/working-with-us-">Working with us</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #523b6b" href="/the-hospice/work-here/current-vacancies">Current vacancies</a></li></ul></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0c709f" href="/the-hospice/study-here">Study here </a><ul class="subs"><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0c709f" href="/the-hospice/study-here/education-support">Education support </a></li></ul></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here">Volunteer here</a><ul class="subs"><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/opportunities">Volunteer Opportunities</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/volunteer-online-application">Volunteer Application Form</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/why-volunteer">Why volunteer?</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/hospice-volunteers">Hospice volunteers</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/retail-volunteers">Retail volunteers</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/schools-students">Schools and students</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/business-leader-volunteers">Business leader volunteers</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/special-skills-volunteers">Special skills volunteers</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/company-volunteering">Company volunteering</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/volunteer-ambassadors">Volunteer ambassadors</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #0ea680" href="/the-hospice/volunteer-here/volunteer-faqs">Volunteer FAQs</a></li></ul></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #76b043" href="/the-hospice/about-us">About us</a><ul class="subs"><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #76b043" href="/the-hospice/about-us/who-we-are">Who we are</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #76b043" href="/the-hospice/about-us/our-history">Our history</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #76b043" href="/the-hospice/about-us/what-we-do">What we do</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #76b043" href="/the-hospice/about-us/our-priorities-and-mission-statement">Our priorities and mission statement</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #76b043" href="/the-hospice/about-us/our-vision-and-values">Our vision and values</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #76b043" href="/the-hospice/about-us/our-financial-model-and-our-performance">Our financial model and our performance</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #76b043" href="/the-hospice/about-us/our-leadership-and-governance">Our leadership and governance</a></li><li><a style="border-left: 6px solid #76b043" href="/the-hospice/about-us/your-concerns-and-feedback">Your concerns and feedback</a></li></ul></li>			</ul>
